trait.text:
Your tiefling might not look like other tieflings. Rather than having the physical characteristics described in the Player's Handbook, choose 1d4 + 1 of the following features:

Small horns;
Fangs or sharp teeth;
A forked tongue;
Catlike eye;
Six fingers on each hand;
Goatlike legs;
Cloven hoofs;
A forked tail;
Leathery or scaly skin;
Red or dark blue skin;
Cast no shadow or reflection;
Exude a smell of brimstone.

